 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#scrunch-vs-semrush-features-monitoring-auditing-and-optimization"&gt;Scrunch vs Semrush Features: Monitoring, Auditing, and Optimization&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
