&lt;ul&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#what-does-it-mean-to-get-indexed-by-chatgpt"&gt;What does it mean to get indexed by ChatGPT?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#but-do-we-know-that-chatgpt-has-a-web-index"&gt;But do we know that ChatGPT has a web index?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#how-to-get-indexed-by-chatgpt"&gt;How to Get Indexed by ChatGPT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#measuring-visibility-in-chatgpt"&gt;Measuring Visibility in ChatGPT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
